726318f-a.title: Queens: Central Avenue - 73rd Street
726318f-a.text:
Central Ave. (foreground), at the N.W. corner of 73rd Street,
showing a small cottage in back of the two story frame house at corner.
This cottage does not show in 1927.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
